name: Cormorant Combat Crate
description:
Cormorant Combat Crate contains everything an eager Caldari combat pilot needs to begin their quest through New Eden.

This special delivery crate includes:

Fully insured Cormorant
Combat fitting for Cormorant
Applicable skills trained to pilot the ship
Cormorant Metalbee SKIN
100 PLEX.

This item cannot be traded or sold on the market.
